Agentidev
=========

This project includes the following bundled third-party components:

SmartClient LGPL Runtime (v14.1p)
---------------------------------
Located at: extension/smartclient/
License: GNU Lesser General Public License v3.0 (LGPLv3)
Source: https://www.smartclient.com/product/download.jsp
License text: extension/smartclient/LICENSE.html

We bundle a subset of the SmartClient LGPL runtime (modules + 5 skins,
~27MB) so the dashboard works on fresh clones without manual SDK setup.

The full SDK is available at smartclient.com for users who want
additional skins, modules, or developer tools. To use a different
SmartClient build, replace the contents of extension/smartclient/
with the corresponding files from your SDK.

Per LGPLv3, you are free to replace this library with a modified
version. The SmartClient runtime is loaded as plain JavaScript files
and can be swapped in place.

